</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20120306060536/http://www.cumbriagridforlearning.org.uk/index.php?category_id=835\">\"Writing Levels at Cumbria Grid for Learning\"</a>. Archived from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cumbriagridforlearning.org.uk/index.php?category_id=835\">the original</a> on 2012-03-06.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Writing+Levels+at+Cumbria+Grid+for+Learning&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cumbriagridforlearning.org.uk%2Findex.php%3Fcategory_id%3D835&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABig+Writing\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">Wilson, Ros (2003). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Strategies-Immediate-Impact-Writing-Standards/dp/0954701909\"><i>Strategies for Immediate Impact on Writing Standards, Usher Street Primary School, Case Study</i></a>. Andrell Education Ltd. p.&#160;1. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/0-9547019-0-9\" title=\"Special:BookSources/0-9547019-0-9\">0-9547019-0-9</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Strategies+for+Immediate+Impact+on+Writing+Standards%2C+Usher+Street+Primary+School%2C+Case+Study&amp;rft.pages=1&amp;rft.pub=Andrell+Education+Ltd&amp;rft.date=2003&amp;rft.isbn=0-9547019-0-9&amp;rft.aulast=Wilson&amp;rft.aufirst=Ros&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.co.uk%2FStrategies-Immediate-Impact-Writing-Standards%2Fd